Ride through mud, rivers and jungle for free medical care
Dr. Georges Bwelle provides free medical care in a rural area in Cameroon
Bwelle and his team spend nearly every weekend seeing hundreds of patients.
There aren&#39;t that many doctors in this West African country - only one in 5,000 people.
