Prepaid mobile phones are subsequently thrown away.
However, there are concerns that small and medium-sized companies remain vulnerable to hacks and surveillance.
In Germany, many of these companies are world market leaders in their particular niche.
“Small and medium-sized companies often lack the experience, staff and financial resources to effectively protect corporate secrets from unauthorized access,” BfV warns in the report.
The US is warning its own companies about economic espionage by other countries.
